metadata.name: theRob
metadata.description:
Visuals by theRob.live is now born in the blockchain.  The image shown here was shot at the top of the Haleakala volcano in Maui.  I hope to bring a fraction of the beauty found in nature to my art and color our world in an inspirational way for everyone to enjoy.
